  "title": "Project Executive (Exhibitions/Events)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>On-site management and client liason is required.</li>\n  <li>To coordinate with clients, suppliers/contractors on projects on all operational matters, and able to trouble-shoot any issues during project.</li>\n  <li>Excellent written communications is required.</li>\n  <li>Able to work with people from all walks of life.</li>\n  <li>Must be able to work on weekends and public holidays when required.</li>\n  <li>Hardworking and able to handle stress.</li>\n  <li>This position will require you to work in various locations around the island as well as in different parts of the world, hence, travelling is necessary.</li>\n  <li>Minimum Diploma level</li>\n  <li>2 years in Exhibitions/Events industry will be an advantage.</li>\n</ul>",
