    "description": "<p>\r\n\tC2 CREATIVE COMMUNICATIONS is a Singapore based company with subsidiary wings in the Middle East and South-East Asia.  We focus on exhibitions and events; mainly working with the MNCs and statutory boards.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\tWith affiliations across 20 countries worldwide, from USA to Europe, Africa, North Asia and South-East Asia, we aim to bring a company's brand name across to the rest of the world with a creative and innovative edge.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\tWith such global presence and services ranging from designing to onsite project management, we have been the one-stop exhibition and events solution for many local and international companies.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>One-stop services we provide internationally include:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n\t<li>\r\n\t\tDesign studio to develop creative competencies in exhibitions as well as event design and branding.</li>\r\n\t<li>\r\n\t\tDesign execution for exhibitions and events</li>\r\n\t<li>\r\n\t\tEvents management and consultancy</li>\r\n\t<li>\r\n\t\tExhibition management and consultancy</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div>\r\n\tAs a team, we understand any companies' business, and deliver their global exhibition and events with pride.</div>\r\n<p>\r\n\t </p>\r\n",
